  "subject": "Modify CSITs for new Prometheus endpoint",
  "commit_message": "Modify CSITs for new Prometheus endpoint\n\nPrometheus is using the ..../prometheus rather than the ...../metrics\nendpoint for statistics now. The ..../metrics end point just returns a\nlist of counters.\n\nThe CSITs are updated to work with this API change on Prometheus.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-4394\nChange-Id: Ia4b9849bf94be6bc0383dc6faef83418554c43f0\nSigned-off-by: liamfallon <liam.fallon@est.tech>\n",
